he two former allies.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Democrats (broad brush) be=
lieve that they know what&#8217;s best and can improve lives through policy=
