h things, you&#8217;ll get more bang for your buck &#8212; not just for inv=
estors and entrepreneurs, but for the government and society at large. Spec=
ifically, I am talking about cheaper energy, more productive manufacturing,=
 cheaper and better drugs and cures, and all of the things that we write ab=
out in Not Boring every week.&#160;&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55,=
 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There&#8217;=
s a &#8220;narcissism of the small difference,&#8221; as Sigmund Freud call=
ed it, between the two groups: &#8220;It is precisely the minor differences=
